{
  "id": "69eef50edf33d3e3d2d99e6a",
  "title": "ページタイトルのパターンを探す",
  "created": 1777267984,
  "updated": 1777303439,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69eef50edf33d3e3d2d99e6a",
      "text": "ページタイトルのパターンを探す",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777267984,
      "updated": 1777268706
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef6cb0000000000931697",
      "text": " ページ名の形式を収集する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268427,
      "updated": 1777268928
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef74a000000000093169a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268554,
      "updated": 1777268554
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef6790000000000931693",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268345,
      "updated": 1777268345
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef50f0000000000931672",
      "text": " 説明的な文章のまま",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777267984,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef64b0000000000931691",
      "text": "  `[井戸端の空気が作った特殊な価値観]`",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268299,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef50f0000000000931674",
      "text": "  [文章形リンク]のことだ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777267984,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef50f0000000000931675",
      "text": " 名詞を修飾したもの",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777267984,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef5ed0000000000931689",
      "text": "  例えば",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268206,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef50f0000000000931676",
      "text": "   [想起の習慣]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268272,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef50f0000000000931677",
      "text": " 単語を造語する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777267984,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef5ea0000000000931688",
      "text": "  例えば",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268203,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef50f0000000000931678",
      "text": "   [/arpla/掠めタグ]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777267984,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef56e000000000093167d",
      "text": " 直接関係していない遠いイメージになぞらえてる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268079,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef574000000000093167e",
      "text": "  この方法だと被りにくい固有の名前がつく",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268084,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef50f0000000000931679",
      "text": "  例えば",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777267984,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef5780000000000931682",
      "text": "   [想起の習慣]というページのタイトルの候補に挙げられた[記憶の陰干し習慣]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268088,
      "updated": 1777268406
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef575000000000093167f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268085,
      "updated": 1777268085
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef803000000000093169f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268740,
      "updated": 1777268740
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef80300000000009316a0",
      "text": "タイトルを考えるときに使えますように",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268740,
      "updated": 1777268776
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef80300000000009316a1",
      "text": " 見つけた現象にタイトルをつけるときにぴったりなものが見つかるまで案を色々出す",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268740,
      "updated": 1777268901
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef83000000000009316af",
      "text": " 例えばここ↓でそうしてる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268784,
      "updated": 1777268857
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef83200000000009316b0",
      "text": "  [想起の習慣#69e79242000000000066aab3]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268786,
      "updated": 1777268861
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef84900000000009316b1",
      "text": "  (先日のタイトル案を出してたあのページが見つかったらここに追加)",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268809,
      "updated": 1777268843
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef82e00000000009316ad",
      "text": "  [募集.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268782,
      "updated": 1777268809
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef80300000000009316a5",
      "text": " すでに存在する語とかならページタイトルの命名に迷わないが",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268740,
      "updated": 1777268740
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef80300000000009316a6",
      "text": "  その単語や文をそのまま使える",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268740,
      "updated": 1777268740
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef80300000000009316a7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268740,
      "updated": 1777268740
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef8fb00000000009316bb",
      "text": "すでにページがあった",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268987,
      "updated": 1777268994
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef8fe00000000009316bd",
      "text": " [ページタイトルのつけかた]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268991,
      "updated": 1777268991
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef7f7b000000000024f5b9",
      "text": " あとで↑にくっつけよう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777303420,
      "updated": 1777303439
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef8fc00000000009316bc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777268988,
      "updated": 1777268988
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef15b00000000000d387cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777276336,
      "updated": 1777276336
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef15b10000000000d387ce",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777276337,
      "updated": 1777276338
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef15b10000000000d387d0",
      "text": "\t議論の発端になった問をページ名にする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777276338,
      "updated": 1777276356
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef15bb0000000000d387d1",
      "text": "\t議論の最中に出てきた光る言葉をページ名にする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777276348,
      "updated": 1777276369
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef15b10000000000d387cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777276338,
      "updated": 1777276338
    }
  ]
}